data.description: Welcome to your DREAM HOME located in a highly desirable location, just minutes away from I-75 access!  With all the upgrades imaginable, this fabulous home is MOVE-IN READY for your family to start creating memories. The main level features a luxurious Master bedroom, providing ultimate convenience. Upstairs, discover three spacious bedrooms, each equipped with WALK-IN closets for ample storage. The heart of this home is the enormous family room, engineered hardwood floors, and a stunning 2-story stone wall gas log fireplace, creating a cozy yet grand atmosphere. The kitchen is a chef's delight with granite countertops, an island featuring an eat-in bar, a pantry, tiled floors, and an abundance of cabinets and countertop space. The breakfast area overlooks the backyard and deck. For more formal occasions, a separate dining room awaits with a charming shiplap wall. On the main floor, find a versatile space that can serve as an office, playroom, or an extra den to suit your family's needs. The private master suite is a retreat, beautiful wood flooring, a walk-in closet, his and hers vanities, a relaxing garden tub, and an oversized shower. Step outside to a large wood privacy fenced yard, complete with a firepit area for outdoor gatherings. The oversized crawl space with concrete flooring offers potential as a workshop area and provides storage galore. The established yard is equipped with a sprinkler system, ensuring a lush and vibrant landscape. Don't miss out on this MUST-SEE home that combines functionality, style, and comfort.  $3,000 Closing costs when you finance with Stacey Frazier with New American Funding.   Schedule a showing today and make this FABULOUS HOME your own!
